I C A R U S

caption.text:
Well, this was seriously the better part of three houses. It wasn't as good as blue lions but better than Rhea's route, definitely better. Characters were the same of course but with new game plus it was easier to improve their skills and power as well as the support ranks. The story was better 'cause we were the "bad appearing but actually good" guys instead of the other way around (where we fought for the actual villain basically... 'till we killed them too). The Final fight wasn't really satisfying (and way easier than in Rhea's route...), this was probably the easiest boss fight in Fire emblem I even had... Except every boss fight in fricking Fates. I was also surprised (with an piece of disappointment) what this route did with Dedue, that was something Dedue would literally never do and I really didn't liked how the blue lions were showed. I'm glad that I saved Felix with recruiting him... And Ashe... And Lysithia from Golden Deers too. Speaking of, next and last route Golden Deers, I'm looking forward to the meme house. This route gets an 7.5/10 © Intelligente Systems, Nintendo, Shouzou Kaga

caption.text:
Novidade WinninGames sua diversão... Nintendo Switch Lite - 32gb Turquesa 
O Switch Lite é o mais novo console da Nintendo, agora em uma versão menor e mais em conta para quem sempre sonhou em ter o mais recente vídeo game portátil da marca. Tem 5,5 polegadas de uma tela touchscreen e resolução de 1280x720, tem dimensões de aproximadamente 9,1 x 20,8 x 1,4 cm e pesa apenas 275g! É a opção ideal para quem prefere jogar fora ou para quem quer jogar online ou localmente no modo multiplayer com algum amigo que tenha o Nintendo Switch, entretanto o Switch lite não se conecta a sua TV. Até 8 consoles podem ser conectados para jogar multiplayer local, sejam eles Switchs da primeira versão ou Lites. A bateria do modelo é de 3750 mAh, dando autonomia de até 6 horas de uso, a memória interna do aparelho é de 32GB! #gamer #games #gaming #gamers #nintendo #nintendo3ds #nintendoswitch #nintendofans #nintendogames #playstation #ps2 #ps3 #ps4 #ps4fat #ps4slim #ps4pro #psvita #psp #xbox #xboxone #xboxones #xboxonex xbox360 #xboxfans #mariobros #sonic #crasbandicot #atibaia #atibaiacity #atibaiasp #modagamer

Novidade WinninGames sua diversão... Zelda Link’s Awekening - Nintendo Switch 
Anos após seu lançamento original para Game Boy, The Legend of Zelda: Link's Awakening traz uma nova experiência para o Nintendo Switch. Tudo começa quando Link perde sua embarcação para uma terrível tempestade e é levado a costa da misteriosa ilha Koholint. Para retornar a sua casa, Link deve superar desafiantes masmorras e combater monstros imponentes.

Esta versão inclui vários elementos presentes no jogo original, como divisões 2D com estilo de plataforma e aparições de personagens que não pertencem a série The Legend of Zelda. A caixa de som portátil Charge4 JBL vai com Bluetooth e espectro total. Ela oferece a possibilidade de amplificar o som com JBL Connect+ com mais de 100 caixas de som compatíveis com a função totalmente sem fios. Além disso, a caixa possui carregador integrado,uma entrada USB que carrega rapidamente seus dispositivos, como smartphone e que garante que você não fique sem bateria nos momentos que mais necessita. Una nueva filtración de GTA6 afirma que el juego se desarrollará en dos ciudades, contará con dos personajes principales e incluso indicará cuándo esperar un anuncio para el juego.
_____

Según el usuario de Reddit, Temperaturerising45, GTA 6 se establecerá en dos ciudades: Las Venturas, con sede en Las Vegas, y San Fierro que es la versión de Rockstar de San Francisco. El filtrador afirma que el mapa será cuatro veces más grande que el presentado en GTA V, y que se incluirán puntos de referencia como el Area 51 y la Presa Hoover.
____

caption.text:
Yesterday, Naughty Dog finally revealed the release date for the highly anticipated PS4 exclusive ‘The Last of Us Part II’.⁣
⁣
Naughty Dog also showed the special editions for the ‘The Last of Us Part II’, and according to the game’s description, the PS4 exclusive will be a 2-disc game.⁣
⁣
That’s gigantic.⁣
⁣
Neil Druckmann, the game’s director said  that ‘The Last of Us Part II’ will be the most ambitious, longest, and biggest game that Naughty Dog has ever put together.⁣
⁣
"𝗪𝐞 𝐛𝐞𝐠𝐚𝐧 𝐰𝐨𝐫𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐨𝐧 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐠𝐚𝐦𝐞 𝐨𝐯𝐞𝐫 𝐟𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐲𝐞𝐚𝐫𝐬 𝐚𝐠𝐨. 𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐝 𝐭𝐨 𝐝𝐞𝐬𝐜𝐫𝐢𝐛𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐢𝐦𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐬𝐞 𝐩𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐬𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐟𝐨𝐥𝐥𝐨𝐰𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐮𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐟𝐢𝐫𝐬𝐭 𝐠𝐚𝐦𝐞. [...] 𝗪𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐰𝐞 𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐳𝐞𝐝 𝐩𝐫𝐞𝐭𝐭𝐲 𝐞𝐚𝐫𝐥𝐲 𝐨𝐧 𝐢𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐰𝐞 𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐞 𝐩𝐮𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐨𝐠𝐞𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫 𝐍𝐚𝐮𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐲 𝐃𝐨𝐠’𝐬 𝐦𝐨𝐬𝐭 𝐚𝐦𝐛𝐢𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐮𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐥𝐨𝐧𝐠𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐠𝐚𝐦𝐞 𝐢𝐧 𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝟑𝟓 𝐲𝐞𝐚𝐫 𝐡𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐲. 𝐓𝐨 𝐭𝐞𝐥𝐥 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐝 𝐨𝐟 𝐬𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐲 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐠𝐚𝐦𝐞 𝐧𝐞𝐞𝐝𝐞𝐝 𝐭𝐨 𝐛𝐞 𝐦𝐚𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐯𝐞.”⁣
⁣
That’s really great news. ⁣
⁣
To put it in context, 2013’s ‘The Last of Us’ won over 200 Game of the Year awards, and the studio is yet to release a game that doesn't immediately become critically and commercially acclaimed.⁣
⁣
Tomorrow is Outbreak Day, and more will be revealed.⁣

caption.text:
Game Freak’s upcoming RPG Little Town Hero has received a new short trailer. At 30 seconds, it offers a brief view of the monsters you’ll battle and the abilities available in combat. Another video will release on September 27th, hopefully containing more details and gameplay.
.
Little Town Hero takes place in a small village whose denizens are not allowed to leave. Our hero is different – he wants to explore the world and coincidentally, a “Monster” shows up to attack the village. Using a strange Red Stone and help from the townsfolk, our hero will need to fight back against overwhelming forces.
.
With music by Toby Fox of Undertale fame, Little Town Hero is already looking like a solid RPG for the Switch. It’s out on October 16th via the Nintendo eShop and will retail for $24.99.
.

Today’s Game: Dragon Quest Builders 2
Platform: Nintendo Switch
——-
So there is this whole subplot where you are kidnapped by the children of Hargon and taken to a prison island. It’s long and I got through it all, but the whole time I wanted to just get back to exploring the Explorer shores. It was still kind of fun; it introduces new mechanics that should prove interesting in this game, so it wasn’t like time was wasted. The video is the last scene before you escape, there might be some minor spoilers about companions you meet on the island. It was really satisfying to get off the island at the end though.

caption.text:
السلام عليكم ورحمة الله وبركاته
مساء الخير جميعآ 🌹
.
غدآ يوم الخميس في تمام الساعة 6 مساءً بتوقيت السعودية ⏱.
سيتم رفع الحظر عن إنطباعات الإعلاميين الذين قامو بتجربة ثلاث ساعات من الجيمبلاي في حدث "Outbreak Day” الخاص للعبة 🎮.
.
فبعدما رأينا في ليلة البارحة عرض للعبة:
‏"The Last of Us ll”
أريد أن أرى إنطباعاتكم في الكومنتات ومدى حماسكم لها 🔥
.
سأبدأ بإنطباعي بإختصار:
العرض مبهر وشدني من بدايته لنهايته وللأمانة كان مليء بالمفاجآت والتساؤلات وأخيرآ كان تاريخ إطلاق اللعبة كما كانت تتحدث الشائعات ✨
.
بشأن جودة العرض:
•الانميشن والعمق البصري والتنوع البيئي مابين المشمس والمثلج والتفاصيل الصغيرة فكانت ممتازة.
•نظام الإخراج وتنوع المشاهد مابين الدراما والحزن والفرح والحب والإنتقام والكره ممتاز.
•الجرافيكس والرسومات وتفاصيل وتعابير الوجه متقنة بشكل ممتاز جدآ فلا خوف من نوتي دوق بهذا الشأن، مثل مارأينا مع ألعابها السابقة.
.
بشأن الشخصيات:
•ظهور شخصية جول واللحظة التي حركت مشاعر جميع اللاعبين بعد الغموض الذي دار حوله مابين هل هو ميت ام انه حي، ظهر رغم كبر سنه لكنه مازال يتمتع ببنية جسدية وطباع حادة مثلما عرفناه.
•ايلي بعدما كبرت ونضجت واصبحت ذات الـ 19 عام بطلة هذا الجزء تستطيع ان تقاتل كما رأينا في العرض، وتسعى للإنتقام لكن لانعلم لمن ستفرغ جام غضبها.
•الكليكرز والأعداء في هذا الجزء اتوقع انه يوجد فرق بين الأول والثاني وتعددهم واختلاف قوة كل عدو عن الآخر وصعوبة قتالهم.
.
شاركوني في الكومنتات عن إنطباعاتكم وكيف رأيتم العرض !

Picked up Cyber-Cop for the Genesis at Game Trader today in Beaverton, OR. All the retro stuff there was mostly sports titles, but saw a few gems here and there. Everything was cheaply priced too!

Corporation (released as Cyber-Cop in North America) is a video game for Amiga, Atari ST and MS-DOS, later ported to the Mega Drive/Genesis. It was developed for Core Design by Dimension Creative Designs by Bill Allen with graphics and design by Kevin Bulmer.

The PC and Sega versions were published by Virgin Games. Originally released for Amiga in 1990, it is one of the earliest 3D first-person shooter games, predating ID Software's Wolfenstein 3D (1992). It was also the first of its kind to utilize dynamic lighting. Gameplay was very complex for its time, featuring role-playing, stealth and hacking elements, similar to the later System Shock and Deus Ex series of games. (Source @wikipedia)

Hey fellow gamers!
First of all, it's HUMP DAYYYY!
Second, you guys wanted more so here's more. You asked and I'm here to answer 😊😊😊 My all time favorite gaming system is the Gamecube. I WILL fight anyone to the death to defend its honor😂 That console is legendary. I play smash with a GC controller to this day.

My horoscope is Saggitarius♐

You guys really want to know my all time favorite game. It's Smash. I grew up on it. I love any game like it too. Mortal Kombat, Harvest Moon, and Animal Crossing all surprisingly fought for my favorite too 😝

I'm most excited for 2020 to brint us Animal Crossing: New Leaf!!! I was asked for my favorite Luigi meme but thought my cutely hideous Luigi keychain would be funny to share, too😂 I love Luigi!

My console of choice is a Gamecube. No surprise there.🎮 I included a closeup of my face tattoo for everyone asking what it says! ☺
Lastly, I don't know how many tattoos I have, so here's my most recent one from Friday the 13th!

caption.text:
Last week was #weekofgameguides and I didn‘t participate because I only have O N E guide book. It is this Pokémon Let‘s Go one. ⁣
Before getting this I didn‘t realize guide books could be more than just... guide books. This one also includes an interview as well as some concept art. I‘ll definitely look out for more books like this for longer games I want to invest some time in. It definitely enhances the gaming experience in a way. ⁣
I‘m currently suffering from a mild case of Pokémon fatigue. Maybe it‘s because I know the general story of the game so well. I don‘t know what the newer entries in the series are like, but this original one... can get a little too grindy for me. I’m taking a break from it for now but I‘m sure I‘ll return to it eventually. ⁣
⁣⁣⁣

A LucasArts ficou famosa nos anos 90 por seus jogos de Point and Click e um dos títulos mais amados por todos foi o Grim Fandango. O jogo é derivado da comemoração mexicana do Dia de los Muertos, onde nosso protagonista deve descobrir quem está por trás de uma cadeia de corrupção no Mundo dos Mortos e é válido lembrar que esse foi o primeiro título em 3D lançado pela empresa. Em 2015 tivemos uma desmaterialização de Grim Fandango que incluía também legendas e dublagem em português do Brasil. Quem não teve a chance de jogar, fica a dica de um jogo divertido e com uma temática atípica nos videogames.
